    "description": {
      "value": "<p>This staff can be wielded as a magic quarterstaff that grants a +2 bonus to attack and damage rolls made with it. While holding it, you gain a +2 bonus to AC, saves, and spell attack rolls.</p><p>The staff has 20 charges and regains [[/r 2d8 + 4]] expended charges daily at dawn. If you expend the last charge, roll a d20. On a 1, the staff retains its +2 bonus to attack and damage rolls but loses all other properties. On a 20, the staff regains [[/r 1d8 + 2]] charges. The staff has the following additional properties:</p><p><em><strong>Power Strike.</strong></em> When you hit with a melee attack using the staff, you can expend 1 charge as part of your Attack action to deal an extra [[/damage 1d6 force]] to the target.</p><p><em><strong>Spells.</strong></em> While holding this staff, you can use an action to expend 1 or more of its charges to cast one of the following spells from it, using your spell save DC and spell attack bonus: <em>@UUID[Compendium.black-flag.spells.Item.HqhvoepCCJSfLoOr]{cone of cold}</em> (5 charges), <em>@UUID[Compendium.black-flag.spells.Item.VYvD59yJYefhAwOI]{fireball}</em> (5th-circle version, 5 charges), <em>@UUID[Compendium.black-flag.spells.Item.gJaou3m2b9pdVA1Q]{globe of invulnerability}</em> (6 charges), <em>@UUID[Compendium.black-flag.spells.Item.09Sensm5KJcvLdhx]{greater hold}</em> (5 charges), <em>@UUID[Compendium.black-flag.spells.Item.0iiu16z9T1sNdNXP]{levitate}</em> (2 charges), <em>@UUID[Compendium.black-flag.spells.Item.RIOCsdRfuC31r9Rf]{lightning bolt}</em> (5th-circle version, 5 charges), <em>@UUID[Compendium.black-flag.spells.Item.RBoSYpr3alIlLBro]{magic missile}</em> (1 charge), <em>@UUID[Compendium.black-flag.spells.Item.V8TvqGWojL1ucfUZ]{ray of enfeeblement}</em> (1 charge), or <em>@UUID[Compendium.black-flag.spells.Item.tXnBDlCTKcRlzn8w]{wall of force}</em> (5 charges).</p><p><em><strong>Retributive Strike.</strong></em> You can use an action to break the staff over your knee or against a solid surface, performing a retributive strike. The staff is destroyed and releases its remaining magic in an explosion that expands to fill a 30-foot-radius sphere centered on it.</p><p>You have a 50 percent chance to instantly travel to a random plane of existence, avoiding the explosion. If you fail to avoid the effect, you take force damage equal to 16 Ã— the number of charges in the staff.</p><p>Every other creature in the area must make a [[/save 17 DEX]]. On a failed save, a creature takes an amount of damage based on how far away it is from the point of origin, as shown in the following table. On a successful save, a creature takes half as much damage.</p><p>@Embed[Compendium.black-flag.rules.JournalEntry.PBo9j135EucIDliX.JournalEntryPage.oDtGdauFgUvygCw4 inline]</p>",
